 <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-4">
 About <span class="whitespace-nowrap"><span class="highlight-line text-brandBlue">WOWOH</span><span class="text-brandOrange">COOL</span></span><br>
 <span class="block text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-slate-700 mt-3 normal-case italic tracking-tight">Shenzhen OEM/ODM Charger Manufacturer Since 2013</span>
 </h1>
 <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium border-l-4 border-brandOrange pl-6 mb-4">
 We are <strong>Dong Yi Technology Co., Ltd</strong>, a professional OEM/ODM manufacturer of wireless chargers, power banks, GaN chargers, and car chargers in Shenzhen, China since 2013.
 </p>
 <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-4">
 ISO 9001 certified factory with a 5,000㎡ facility, 4 automated SMT production lines, and 1M+ monthly capacity. Every product is CE, FCC, RoHS, and Qi2 certified for global market compliance. Our 50+ R&D engineers specialize in GaN V, PD 3.1, Qi2 MPP, and semi-solid-state battery technologies — featured at CES 2026. We have delivered 10M+ units to 200+ global brands including Bosch and Jacob Jensen. <a href="/service" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">Learn about our OEM/ODM services</a>.
 </p>
